---
title: "_applyAllowlistedTargetsUpdates (WorkflowRouter)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_wf: check workflowId allowlisted
    q_check_wf --> q_check_empty: s_allowlistedWorkflowIds.contains(workflowId)
    q_check_wf --> q_revert_wf: workflowId not allowlisted
    q_revert_wf --> [*]: revert WorkflowIdNotAllowlisted(workflowId)

    q_check_empty --> q_iter_removes: removes.length > 0 OR adds.length > 0
    q_check_empty --> q_revert_empty: removes.length == 0 AND adds.length == 0
    q_revert_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList()

    q_iter_removes --> q_remove_target: i < removes.length
    q_iter_removes --> q_iter_adds: i >= removes.length (done)

    q_remove_target --> q_cast_selectors: target = removes[i]
    q_cast_selectors --> q_remove_selectors: cast allowlistedSelectors bytes32[] to bytes4[] via assembly
    q_remove_selectors --> q_remove_set: _applyAllowlistedSelectorsUpdates(workflowId, target, allSelectors, empty)
    q_remove_set --> q_emit_target_remove: s_workflowInfos[workflowId].allowlistedTargets.remove(target)
    q_emit_target_remove --> q_iter_removes: emit TargetRemovedFromAllowlist, i++

    q_iter_adds --> q_add_target: i < adds.length
    q_iter_adds --> [*]: i >= adds.length (done)

    q_add_target --> q_check_zero_addr: target = adds[i].target
    q_check_zero_addr --> q_add_set: target != address(0)
    q_check_zero_addr --> q_revert_zero: target == address(0)
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress()

    q_add_set --> q_add_selectors: allowlistedTargets.add(target)
    q_add_selectors --> q_iter_adds: _applyAllowlistedSelectorsUpdates(workflowId, target, empty, selectors), i++

    note right of q_cast_selectors
        INV-001: assembly cast bytes32[] to bytes4[] is safe because both are in-memory 32-byte slot arrays
        INV-002: removing target first removes all its selectors via _applyAllowlistedSelectorsUpdates
    end note

    note right of q_add_set
        INV-003: allowlistedTargets.add is idempotent (EnumerableSet)
        INV-004: address(0) target is rejected
    end note
